msgid "2. <b>入口保护：</b>系统已自动封锁 wp-login.php 和 wp-admin 目录。请使用 <code>[sba_login_box]</code> 短代码在前台展示登录面板。"
msgstr "2. <b>Entry Protection:</b> wp-login and wp-admin are blocked. Use <code>[sba_login_box]</code> shortcode for front-end login."

msgid "3. <b>IP 信任：</b>看仪表盘 IP。若为 127.0.0.1 或内网 IP，请根据 CDN/代理环境切换至「Nginx」或「Cloudflare」。"
msgstr "3. <b>IP Trust:</b> Check Dashboard IP. If 127.0.0.1, change source to Nginx or Cloudflare."

msgid "4. <b>AJAX 补丁：</b>无痕访问首页。若「访客轨迹」未增加记录，说明 PHP 被静态缓存截断，此时必须开启。"
msgstr "4. <b>AJAX Patch:</b> Enable this if visitor tracks aren't updating due to static caching."

msgid "5. <b>爬虫防御：</b>「Cookie 校验」识别无状态脚本。内置「蜜罐陷阱」会自动诱捕并封禁扫描页面的恶意爬虫。"
msgstr "5. <b>Anti-Bot:</b> Cookie check identifies scripts. Honeypot traps and bans scanners automatically."

